NO；<br />\n7) 每周到深水埗警署報到四次<br />\n8) 居於報稱地址"},{"pid":"1a9066aa861207b5e0a7fe91b8299ccb74f0bbf8","tid":2447161,"uid":263648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"00a94862bd68e9b5ec892df7e4a6ac3f006fb950","tid":2447161,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:25:23.000Z","msg":"【即時】(12:24) 初選47人案，高等法院駁回律政司就何啟明的保釋覆核，何啟明獲准保釋外出。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:42:10.000Z","msg":"玩咩？高院扮正義？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都無曬公信力"},{"pid":"aa9643486673ba7106da01853e8f28c856f84bd6","tid":2447161,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:43:56.000Z","msg":"溫和組織都大機會可以保<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb64b8e5029631895337efc1062b449769736eb8","tid":2447161,"uid":63782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa9643486673ba7106da01853e8f28c856f84bd6","tid":2447161,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:43:56.000Z","msg":"溫和組織都大機會可以保<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:48:07.000Z","msg":"睇心情亂鳩咁批啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n民主黨嗰班冇簽落墨仲溫和過民協咪一樣冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eceb58bad3e802f8af78905bb5538685cfdf2229","tid":2447161,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T05:00:09.000Z","msg":"如果佢都可以保釋<br />\n咁施德來更加有機會可以保釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf9a173a6716c674f2c8afd37925391e2d8cf184","tid":2447161,"uid":125385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eceb58bad3e802f8af78905bb5538685cfdf2229","tid":2447161,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T05:00:09.000Z","msg":"如果佢